<subSubSection pageId="1" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1436,1398,1711]" pageId="1">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,273,1398,1423]" pageId="1">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Among Afrotropical genera 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pasteels" authorityYear="1969" box="[600,773,1398,1423]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Cyphanthidium" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[600,773,1398,1423]" italics="true" pageId="1">Cyphanthidium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
can be recognized by the combination of extensive yellow maculations in both sexes, aroliae present, preoccipital margin not carinate, omaulus either not carinate or carinate only dorsally, male S5 broadly, shallowly emarginate and with small apicolateral spine, and female with fourtoothed mandible and scopa.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1436,1398,1711]" pageId="1">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pasteels" authorityYear="1969" box="[199,369,1542,1567]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Cyphanthidium" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[199,369,1542,1567]" italics="true" pageId="1">Cyphanthidium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has the megachiliform shape and general coloration of many Afrotropical 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Michener" authorityYear="1948" box="[1217,1364,1542,1567]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Afranthidium" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1217,1364,1542,1567]" italics="true" pageId="1">Afranthidium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
but is readily distinguished by the presence of arolia and the four-toothed female mandible (Michener 2007). The recent molecular phylogeny of Litman 
<emphasis box="[514,564,1614,1639]" italics="true" pageId="1">et al</emphasis>
. (2016) placed 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pasteels" authorityYear="1969" box="[742,912,1614,1639]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Cyphanthidium" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[742,912,1614,1639]" italics="true" pageId="1">Cyphanthidium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Cockerell" authorityYear="1900" box="[993,1132,1614,1639]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Dianthidium" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[993,1132,1614,1639]" italics="true" pageId="1">Dianthidium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group, in a well-supported clade that included 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Michener" authorityYear="1948" box="[380,543,1650,1675]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Icteranthidium" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[380,543,1650,1675]" italics="true" pageId="1">Icteranthidium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Popov" authorityYear="1950" box="[562,704,1650,1675]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Eoanthidium" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[562,704,1650,1675]" italics="true" pageId="1">Eoanthidium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Cockerell" authorityYear="1904" box="[723,865,1650,1675]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Anthidiellum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[723,865,1650,1675]" italics="true" pageId="1">Anthidiellum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Friese" authorityYear="1905" box="[883,1063,1650,1675]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Pachyanthidium" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[883,1063,1650,1675]" italics="true" pageId="1">Pachyanthidium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pasteels" authorityYear="1969" box="[1083,1193,1650,1675]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Benanthis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1083,1193,1650,1675]" italics="true" pageId="1">Benanthis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Cameron" authorityYear="1905" box="[1211,1377,1650,1675]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Plesianthidium" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1211,1377,1650,1675]" italics="true" pageId="1">Plesianthidium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Isensee" authorityYear="1927" box="[151,321,1686,1711]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Rhodanthidium" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[151,321,1686,1711]" italics="true" pageId="1">Rhodanthidium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. All of these genera, except 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Isensee" authorityYear="1927" box="[634,804,1686,1711]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Rhodanthidium" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[634,804,1686,1711]" italics="true" pageId="1">Rhodanthidium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, include Afrotropical species.
</paragraph>
